  "title": "MIAYBE 1.3 Dashboard Schema",
  "description": "JSON Schema for a data entry dashboard compliant with MIAYBE 1.3 (Minimum Information About Your Bioprocessing Experiment). Generated from specification dated 2026-02-10. Fields tagged with MIAYBE status: R=required, M=recommended, O=optional.",
